===Noun===
'''salmagundi'''
# A [[mixture]] of chopped [[meat]] and pickled [[herring]], with [[oil]], [[vinegar]], [[pepper]], and [[onion]]s.
# Hence, a mixture of various [[ingredient]]s; an [[olio]] or [[medley]]; a [[potpourri]]; a [[miscellany]].

